                                  "NodeIsActive": true,
                                  "NodePortraitBitmap": "",
                                  "NodeNpcName": "",
                                  "NodeSound": "none",
                                  "conversationText": "As <he/she> pondered the question, <he/she> thought <he/she> felt a coolness in the breeze, the merest ghost of a ghost of winter or evening or some time long ago. Yes, <he/she> was desperate; but who wasn't desperate, in their own way? An idle intelligence that was not <his/her> own seemed to glance into <his/her> heart, and in doing so considered its own. Why must all longings be denied or diminished or utterly destroyed? What forbade presence from holding desire and its object at the same time?",
